A little of what grandmarc
has waiting for you...

Welcome to grandmarc Adelaide Hills, a place designed to enrich the health, happiness and wellbeing of everyone who chooses to call it home.

From the larger allotments and our focus on natural open spaces and active lifestyles to the proposed community farm and market café, function centre and B&B, we’ve been looking at all sorts of ways to make living in grandmarc something truly special.

We invite you to share our vision for a flourishing community that will continue to grow, evolve and foster a spirit unique to grandmarc.

Discover life in grandmarc

There's plenty to discover about grandmarc, from our vision for an engaged and active community to our focus on diverse architecture.

There are many advantages of living in grandmarc and we hope you'll come on this journey to help shape the future of this beautiful pocket of the Adelaide Hills.

Living in grandmarc

Beautiful design with natural flair

We know that individuality in home and garden comes from creative freedom, and that’s something we endeavour to provide to every grandmarc resident.

Our personalised design service is a significant point of difference and it helps us better understand your idea of a dream home, while allowing you to be bold and to inject your own personality and style into your living environment.

Design + Build Philosophy

Close to everything

grandmarc is close to a range of enjoyable recreational activities including farmers markets, wineries & cellar doors, activities for the kids and plenty of other things to see and do to support a healthy and active lifestyle.

To uncover the delights of the Adelaide Hills we encourage you to explore nearby.
